{"word":"H3607 - כָּלָא - kâlâʼ - kaw-law' - Finish","slug":"H3607","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּלָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kâlâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Finish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D0; - ka&#x0302;la&#x0302;'</b> - <i>kaw-law'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>restrict</i>, by act (<i>hold</i> back or in) or word (<i>prohibit</i>): - finish, forbid, keep (back), refrain, restrain, retain, shut up, be stayed, withhold."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3608\">H3608</a>, <a href=\"#/H3609\">H3609</a>, <a href=\"#/H3610\">H3610</a>, <a href=\"#/H3628\">H3628</a>, <a href=\"#/H4356\">H4356</a>"}]}